summary:
Betty comforts Bruce after his aunt’s death.

 I thought about doing this since yesterday. This set is taken place during...
caption:
Betty comforts Bruce after his aunt’s death.

I thought about doing this since yesterday. This set is taken place during early-mid 90’s as you can see. Betty Ross sees Bruce, whom she attends Harvard University with him during this time, after his aunt, Elaine, died from a car accident.

During this, Betty comforts Bruce about his loss and opens up to him about her strained relationship with her father and the death of her mother. This would show their growing closer and closer.
